{"thag6.8:0.1":"Theragatha 6.8 ","thag6.8:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thag6.8:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag6.8:0.4":"Migajalattheragatha ","thag6.8:1.1":"“Sudesito cakkhumata, ","thag6.8:1.2":"buddhenadiccabandhuna; ","thag6.8:1.3":"Sabbasamyojanatito, ","thag6.8:1.4":"sabbavattavinasano. ","thag6.8:2.1":"Niyyaniko uttarano, ","thag6.8:2.2":"tanhamulavisosano; ","thag6.8:2.3":"Visamulam aghatanam, ","thag6.8:2.4":"chetva papeti nibbutim. ","thag6.8:3.1":"Annanamulabhedaya, ","thag6.8:3.2":"kammayantavighatano; ","thag6.8:3.3":"Vinnananam pariggahe, ","thag6.8:3.4":"nanavajiranipatano. ","thag6.8:4.1":"Vedananam vinnapano, ","thag6.8:4.2":"upadanappamocano; ","thag6.8:4.3":"Bhavam angarakasumva, ","thag6.8:4.4":"nanena anupassano. ","thag6.8:5.1":"Maharaso sugambhiro, ","thag6.8:5.2":"jaramaccunivarano; ","thag6.8:5.3":"Ariyo atthangiko maggo, ","thag6.8:5.4":"dukkhupasamano sivo. ","thag6.8:6.1":"Kammam kammanti natvana, ","thag6.8:6.2":"vipakanca vipakato; ","thag6.8:6.3":"Paticcuppannadhammanam, ","thag6.8:6.4":"yathavalokadassano; ","thag6.8:6.5":"Mahakhemangamo santo, ","thag6.8:6.6":"pariyosanabhaddako”ti. ","thag6.8:6.7":"… Migajalo thero …. "}